{"title":"【067】字体风格和样式简写","slug":"hell0-world15","date":"2022-10-03T14:30:59.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:17:16.034Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world15.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                font family&size                       font-style:normal,italic,oblique                粗细font-weight","covers":null,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>font family&size</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./mystyle2.css\">  \n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1></h1>\n    <p class=\"p1\"> \n        font-style:normal,italic,oblique\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"p2\">\n        粗细font-weight<span id=\"more\"></span>:属性可是名称，lighter（100）,normal（400）,bold（700）,bolder（900）;数值100-900共9个。\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"p3\">\n       小型大写字符font-variant:normal/small-caps<br><br>\n       可简写，中间空格隔开。如font:oblique 100 small-caps 华文仿宋；但font-size,font-family是必须的。\n    </p><br><br>\n</body>\n</html>","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":30,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[]}